reviewText: We were extremely disappointed in this video. There are much better travel videos out there.

This is the way to check out where you want to go for vacation or a new sailing destination.  Much better than books or travel broachers.  It shows the neighborhoods or areas that would not be safe place to go after night, if there are any bad areas.  It's like have a guide with you while your looking at the sights.
This video may have been released in 2011, but it certainly was not filmed in that year. Very difficult to watch. The information may be factual and helpful, but it was too dated for me to enjoy.
